reviewText: The funniest moments were shown in American Hustle.  The video seemed rushed (like they shot it all in one night) and ill prepared, low budget.  Only for true Red, Luenell and Melanie fans.
Title: Katt Williams Presents: Katthouse Comedy

reviewText: Comedienne Katt Williams has released another raunchy hilarious DVD.  The comediennes featured on this DVD were featured on the 100 city American Hustle Tour.  Black comediennes Luenell, Melanie Comarcho and Red Grant round out the cast of this funny DVD.  Katt Williams serves as the executive producer of the DVD.  Red Grant is probably the most popular of the comediennes featured on the DVD.  Luenell and Melanie Comarcho perform funny routines during the stand up concert DVD.  The running time of the DVD is 65 minutes.
Title: Katt Williams Presents: Katthouse Comedy

reviewText: I am a HUGE Katt Williams fan. I buy things because he is in it. I know all of the comedians on this DVD and have loved their works as well. But this was a little all over the place. A "movie" about the group of comedians traveling together doing shows. Was not long, thank goodness. But, just too corny. I was just disappointed.
Title: Katt Williams Presents: Katthouse Comedy

reviewText: Thanks for sending the correct DVD and it was in excellent condition.Thanks for expediting. This will be an wonderful addition to my collection.
Title: Katt Williams Presents: Katthouse Comedy

reviewText: I love Lunell and Red Grant they are funny as ever I love this darn dvd they had me crying laughing
